# Cloudflare Fundamentals

## Overview
Cloudflare is a global CDN and security platform that helps websites load faster and stay secure.

## Key Services
- CDN (Content Delivery Network)
- DDoS Protection
- DNS Management
- Serverless Workers
- Zero Trust Security

## Beginner Tips
- Start with Workers for small automation
- Use Page Rules to optimize caching
- Always enable SSL/TLS

